  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AcceptRequestConfFrag
    DialogFragment displayed when a Driver wants to accept a request.
    CarDetailsDialog
    DialogFragment displayed when a user signs up as a driver that prompts the user to input their car details
    DisplayQRDialog
    DialogFragment displayed when generating a QR for payment.
    DriverDetailsFragment
    an alert dialog appears on the rider's screen when they click on Driver Details button the alert dialog shows all the information of their driver (name, phone number, car details, driver rating etc) the rider can contact the driver directly from the dialog view
    DriverReviewFragment
    DialogFragment displayed to the Driver when selecting 'Reviews' from the navigation drawer.
    ForgotPasswordDialog
    DialogFragment displayed when the user selects 'Forgot Password' from the sign-in screen.
    RateDriverFrag
    DialogFragment displayed to Riders upon ride completion.
    RideRequestConfFrag
    DialogFragment displayed when a Rider is making a new Request.
    ScanQRDialog
    DialogFragment displayed when scanning a QR for payment.
    SensitiveActionDialog
    DialogFragment displayed for any action that requires re-authentication of user
